SUSTAINABLE AGRICULTURE ADVISOR

This Streamlit app helps farmers predict sustainability scores based on soil, crop, and weather parameters. It provides personlaized recommendations, visual insights, and downloadable reports to promote eco-friendly farming practices.

FEATURES
- Sustainability score prediction
- Personalized farming suggestions
- Visual charts and progress bar
- Downloadable PDF and CSV reports

TECH STACK
- Python
- Streamlit
- scikit-learn
- joblib
- FPDF
- Pandas